  <para>
    Save the definitions of one or more &materials; in a data file.
    All of the &properties; used in the &materials; will be saved as
    well.
  </para>
  <para>
    The <varname>format</varname> is one of the data file formats
    discussed in <xref linkend='Section-Concepts-FileFormats'/>.  The
    <varname>materials</varname> parameter is a <link
      linkend="Object-list">Python list</link> of names
    of &materials;, <foreignphrase>e.g</foreignphrase>,
    <userinput>['granite', 'schist', 'pumice']</userinput>.
  </para>

